rComments: Great teacher, but she is hard, test are challenging but if you study for them you shouldn't have a problem. Make sure your grades on the discussions, quizzes, and Wiley are high enough because that's what is going to carry your grade. Don't be late on those or you will not pass the class.

Looking at ACCY 302 professors, I'm not sure I could recommend you take it with Drnevich. She does not give students any flexibility in anything! While the class allowed me to learn more about accounting, I feel I would have been better off with a different professor.
